dct_title_s: Energy map of central Asia / produced and distributed by Petroleum Economist in association with Ernst & Young ; designed by D.A. Burles (Cover Panel)
dct_description_sm: "June 1993." Shows oil and gas fields, pipelines, refineries,tanker terminals, hydro-electric power facilities, coal-producing areas, and nuclear power plants. Includes lists of names of fields and basins. Panel title. Location map in panel on verso.
